072c26a101277c2fba0bd","tid":283980,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T16:07:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔係八仙大火個生還者咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n卡碧呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都咁多年啦 仲要屈佢 真係好無恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之前佢又唔出黎告人誹謗<br />\n真係有啲鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5d2659267a1a73df52855623bfcecfa29d05d97","tid":283980,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T16:20:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>緊係莊豐源案啦。仆街<br />\n成個香港輸晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為人大䆁法而唔係修改基本法？</blockquote><br />\n都冇釋法。<br />\n<br />\n在莊豐源案終審判決前，香港特區政府曾經請求終審法院根據《基本法》第158條提請全國人民代表大會常務委員會解釋《基本法》，不過終審法院沒有採納。[14]終審法院在2001年7月20日判決政府敗訴後，特區政府表示對判決失望，但是會尊重判決及採取適當措施執行判決。"},{"pid":"180dd86aeb60d43b2feb956b8104b9db6d632978","tid":283980,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T16:28:24.000Z","msg":"紙盒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8684fda2c42d406de51b1c425487e2841628648","tid":283980,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T16:29:43.000Z","msg":"即刻諗起歐陽炳強，坐咁廿年都係話自己無辜，當年啲法證技術又未咁先進。"},{"pid":"7eae51385af74156eac5ba328a63bebc7eda5c62","tid":283980,"uid":1346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T16:31:52.000Z","msg":"第一時間都係諗到歐陽炳強"},{"pid":"a6b6794a86a69b9d0878dccba15f54889cf5ab8b","tid":283980,"uid":38271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T16:47:23.000Z","msg":"全港市民熱烈慶祝回歸案"},{"pid":"dd7fac98c830264e9f0565fb7917ed39f2c2ed43","tid":283980,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T16:49:06.000Z","msg":"歐陽炳強同徐步高"},{"pid":"5e785eb06d600ee3418f7234651e07dcb10f61c7","tid":283980,"uid":26847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T16:50:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>見到標題即刻諗起歐陽炳強</blockquote><br />\n草率結案，咁就毀人一世</blockquote><br />\n佢係第一單用科學鑑證判罪，<br />\n記得之前睇過有人話如果判佢無罪的話，<br />\n科學鑑證既公信力就會低左好多<br />\n<br />\n同埋我都覺得結案好求其，<br />\n又淨係集中查佢一個，<br />\n但其實仲有好多疑點，咁都入到罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b5af47b67be0a2693f4f83287b43081c180fafd","tid":283980,"uid":9542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T16:50:43.000Z","msg":"大圍單智障人士案"},{"pid":"ce2f3e8f44fd7596d0d1c6fd90aac8fa5cd4c433","tid":283980,"uid":50658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T16:50:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>歐陽炳強同徐步高</blockquote><br />\n嗰陣仲有睇雲海分析單案<br />\n真係好可疑"},{"pid":"1cbe7d8509fbfa3d4fdcb7d817751cdab2fb66cf","tid":283980,"uid":36300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T16:51:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mI1iXKmsU3w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmI1iXKmsU3w&d=J0GRqAjvQu%2FjMp8tb0%2BH7dtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=d7c71a64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mI1iXKmsU3w</a><br />\n<br />\n危險人物 - 紙盒藏屍案(跑馬地紙盒藏屍案)"},{"pid":"32014612d5fd1d4c9f2558449fec8b187949e01b","tid":283980,"uid":109263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T17:14:05.000Z","msg":"香港市民普遍支持民主回歸"},{"pid":"20161c92718e0d2a38f3da1a555df20acefb163d","tid":283980,"uid":36300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T17:45:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/XRXIu-wL-N0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FXRXIu-wL-N0&d=J0GRqAjvQu%2FjMp8tb0%2BH7dtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=5e948d85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/XRXIu-wL-N0</a>"},{"pid":"080b512782af75849e0e